ation (CPU/memory requests and limits) for the Istio sidecar proxies (`istio-proxy`) and the `adservice` container to ensure they are not being throttled under load. 3. Monitor node health, particularly memory usage on `node-6`, to identify and mitigate resource exhaustion that can impact pod performance. 4. Enhance alerting to specifically trigger on increases in DNS resolution latency/errors and on `istio_request_duration` metrics across the service mesh.", 'metadata': {'source_file': 'market_root_cause_reports_en_6mtd.jsonl', 'original_source': 'adservice failure at 2022-03-20 08:48:49', 'system_type': 'Banking Microservice (service)', 'component': 'adservice', 'metrics': ['GC', 'heap', 'latency', 'memory', 'network', 'rt', 'thread'], 'root_cause_category': 'The root cause of the incident was container network latency in the `adservice` service, beginning at approximately 2022-03-20 08:48:49 UTC+8. Evidenc'}, 'score': 0.43817901611328125}]
